---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Jak to funguje – H2OPE" description="Strukturovaný proces od prvního kontaktu po průběžnou podporu. Zjistěte, jak vodíková terapie H2OPE funguje.">

  <!-- BANNER -->
  <div class="page-banner">
    <div class="container">
      <h1><span class="cs-only">Jak to funguje</span><span class="en-only">How It Works</span></h1>
      <p><span class="cs-only">Strukturovaný proces od prvního kontaktu po průběžnou podporu.</span><span class="en-only">Structured process from first contact to ongoing support.</span></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- TIMELINE -->
  <section class="timeline-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="timeline">

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-step">
            <div class="step-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="step-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <span class="step-label"><span class="cs-only">Krok 1</span><span class="en-only">Step 1</span></span>
            <h2><span class="cs-only">Konzultace nebo Workshop</span><span class="en-only">Consultation or Workshop</span></h2>
            <p><span class="cs-only">Přijedeme za vámi, vše vám ukážeme a společně nastavíme.<br />(poskytujeme také individuální konzultace)</span><span class="en-only">We'll come to you, show you everything, and set it up together.<br />(we also provide individual consultations)</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-step">
            <div class="step-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 2.83l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 0 1-4 0v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 0 1-2.83-2.83l.06-.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.68 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 0 1 0-4h.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 2.83-2.83l.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 4.68a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1-1.51V3a2 2 0 0 1 4 0v.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 2.83 2.83l-.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 19.4 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.51 1H21a2 2 0 0 1 0 4h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51 1z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="step-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <span class="step-label"><span class="cs-only">Krok 2</span><span class="en-only">Step 2</span></span>
            <h2><span class="cs-only">Nastavení FlowGen</span><span class="en-only">FlowGen Setup</span></h2>
            <p><span class="cs-only">Propojíme vás s naší aplikací pro sledování individuálního pokroku.</span><span class="en-only">We'll connect you with our app for tracking individual progress.</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-step">
            <div class="step-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="step-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <span class="step-label"><span class="cs-only">Krok 3</span><span class="en-only">Step 3</span></span>
            <h2><span class="cs-only">Pronájem stroje</span><span class="en-only">Machine Rental</span></h2>
            <p><span class="cs-only">Pronajmete si od nás stroj k vám do kanceláře nebo přímo domů, abyste mohli pravidelně využívat benefitů vodíku.</span><span class="en-only">You rent a machine from us to your office or directly home, so you can regularly benefit from hydrogen.</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-step">
            <div class="step-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div class="step-line"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <span class="step-label"><span class="cs-only">Krok 4</span><span class="en-only">Step 4</span></span>
            <h2><span class="cs-only">Pravidelná vodíková sezení</span><span class="en-only">Regular Hydrogen Sessions</span></h2>
            <p><span class="cs-only">Absolvujete vodíková sezení dle vašeho plánu.</span><span class="en-only">You complete hydrogen sessions according to your plan.</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-item">
          <div class="timeline-step">
            <div class="step-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/><line x1="2" y1="20" x2="22" y2="20"/></svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-content">
            <span class="step-label"><span class="cs-only">Krok 5</span><span class="en-only">Step 5</span></span>
            <h2>H2OPE Score</h2>
            <p><span class="cs-only">Analyzujeme data a optimalizujeme program.</span><span class="en-only">We analyze data and optimize the program.</span></p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-wrap">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-card">
        <p class="cta-pre"><span class="cs-only">Nejste si jistí jak vám vodík pomůže?</span><span class="en-only">Not sure how hydrogen can help you?</span></p>
        <h2><span class="cs-only">Pojďme se spojit na 15 min, kde Vám vše ukážeme a vysvětlíme</span><span class="en-only">Let's connect for 15 min and we'll show and explain everything</span></h2>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-orange" data-open-modal="contact"><span class="cs-only">Chci nezávaznou konzultaci</span><span class="en-only">I want a free consultation</span> →</button>
        <p class="cta-note"><span class="cs-only">Konzultace je nezávazná. Lidský přístup.</span><span class="en-only">Consultation is free. Human approach.</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .timeline-section { padding: 5rem 0; }

  .timeline { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .timeline-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline-step {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .step-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    background: rgba(0, 180, 216, 0.13);
    color: var(--cyan);
    border-radius: 14px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .step-icon svg {
    width: 26px;
    height: 26px;
  }

  .step-line {
    width: 2px;
    flex: 1;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--cyan), transparent);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    min-height: 60px;
  }

  .timeline-content {
    padding: 0 0 3rem;
  }

  .step-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--cyan);
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    padding-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  .timeline-content h2 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--blue);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .timeline-content p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--gray);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  /* HIGHLIGHTS */
  .highlights-section { padding: 5rem 0; }
  .highlights-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
  .highlight-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(26,58,92,0.07);
    transition: transform 0.25s;
  }
  .highlight-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }
  .highlight-icon { font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .highlight-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--blue); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .highlight-card p { font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6; }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .timeline-item { grid-template-columns: 56px 1fr; gap: 1.25rem; }
    .step-icon { width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 10px; }
    .step-icon svg { width: 22px; height: 22px; }
    .highlights-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .timeline-content { padding-bottom: 2rem; }
    .cta-card { padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>
